        // The maximum number of teams is limited by three factors:
        // 1. The minimum of coders and mathematicians available (each team needs at least one of each).
        // 2. The total number of students divided by 3 (each team needs 3 students).
        // 3. The sum of coders and mathematicians, as 'x' students can only fill the third slot.
        //    If we have k teams, we need at least k coders and k mathematicians.
        //    The remaining k students (to make 3k total) can be filled by 'x' students
        //    or by additional coders/mathematicians.
